Ebola haemorrhagic fever in Uganda - WHO Update 13
--------------------------------------------------
As of Sun 29 Oct 2000, the Ugandan Ministry of Health has reported 211 cases
of Ebola haemorrhagic fever, including 72 deaths. [This represents an
increase of 6 cases and one death during the past 24 hours. - Mod.CP
--
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
